name: Streetlights
description:
Footage taken on 07/15/20 from the switching color lights under a bridge on my hometown Pachuca, Hidalgo. 

I was coming back home from recording urban footage and right when i was about to go inside i saw these lights switching colors under a bridge, i thought about crossing or not for a bit cause where the lights are its a place that you cannot access safely, you have to cross the highway fast and it was late at night so i didnt want to get mugged neither hehe but everything was cool i recorded the lights switching colors for like 10-15 minutes and made it back home safely - then edited on 04/27/21 on a sunny afternoon, most likely very high.
